Trinity::
She was looking at herself in the water. She was admiring her 
reflection and smiling. Then a tail splashed and rippled the water. 
It was a fish. She growled "Hey! That wasn't very nice."  She let out 
her kitten roar and swatted at the fish in the water. The fish just 
swam away. "Get back here you. I'm a fierce predacon. And your going 
to be dinner." She leaned over and tried to swat at the fish, even 
though it was a few yards away. She leaned over a little further, 
trying to reach the fish.  Her paws slipped on the wet grass, and she 
fell into the pond.  She splashed around and her head went under 
water. She came back up to the surface, choking and splashing, trying 
to keep her head above the water. "HELP!"  her went under and then 
came back up. She coughed and sputtered. "HEL.." Her head went back 
under the water. She couldn't swim.
